(348, 'New Executive Admin Notification', 'super_admin_templates', 'AutomotoHR.com', 'accounts@automotohr.com', '', 'Your new AutomotoHR platform Executive Admin log in information', '', '<p>Dear {{firstname}} {{lastname}},<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Team at AutomotoHR would like to welcome and introduce you to your new AutomotoHR Talent management and hiring platform.​</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your Username: {{username}}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use the following link to {{create_password_link}}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your account will be activated and ready, as soon as you create your new password, opening a whole new world of opportunities to:</strong> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1</strong>- Build your Company Career pages in minutes<br />\r\n<strong>2</strong>- Post to all of your preferred job boards<br />\r\n<strong>3</strong>- Hire on the go with your mobile optimized hiring system<br />\r\n<strong>4</strong>- Easily evaluate candidates and collaborate with teams to make the best hire<br />\r\n<strong>5</strong>- Maintain all of your Companies pertinent and legally required hiring information, government compliance forms and data all in one place, with a single secure log in.<br />\r\n<strong>6</strong>- Complete easily managed Onboarding process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a link for you to log in  <a href=\"https://www.automotohr.com/login\"><strong>https://www.automotohr.com/login</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>This account is an Executive admin level account, so when you are on the log in screen you will need to click the button that says \"Executive Admin Login\" which will take you to the correct log in area.</strong></em>  </p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also find your \"Employee login” located in the footer of your company Career page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe are here to help you Succeed!!<br />\r\nPlease Email or Call us any time with your questions or comments.<br />\r\nWe would love to hear from