(349, 'New Employee Team Member Notification', 'super_admin_templates', 'AutomotoHR.com', 'accounts@automotohr.com', '', 'Your new AutomotoHR platform Employee login information', '', '<p>Dear {{firstname}} {{lastname}},<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Team at AutomotoHR would like to welcome and introduce you to your new AutomotoHR Talent management and hiring platform.​</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your Username: {{username}}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use the following link to {{create_password_link}}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your account will be activated and ready to use, as soon as you have created your new password, opening a whole new world of opportunities:</strong> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a link for you to log in  <a href=\"https://www.automotohr.com/login\"><strong>https://www.automotohr.com/login</strong></a>  </p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also find your <strong>\"Employee login” </strong>screen located in the footer of your company Career page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe are here to help you Succeed!!<br />\r\nPlease Email or Call us any time with your questions or comments.<br />\r\nWe would love to hear from you.<br />\r\nThank You</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The AutomotoHR Team </strong>   <br />\r\nAutomotoHR.com</p>\r\n\r\n<h5><strong>Customer Service And Technical Support</strong></h5>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>(888) 794-0794 ext 2</li>\r\n <li><u><a href=\"mailto:Support@AutomotoHR.com\"> Support@AutomotoHR.com</a></u></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n <tbody>\r\n  <tr>\r\n   <td>You are receiving this email to confirm an action you have taken on AutomotoHR.com. <strong><a href=\"mailto:Accounts@AutomotoHR.com?subject=Unsubscribe&body=Please remove my information from any further mailings\" tabindex=\"-1\" target=\"_parent\">Unsubscribe</a></strong></td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n   <td> </td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n   <td>If you need assis